block append section 
  link(rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/module_content.css")
  section.container-2
    h2 TriAge Challenge Education (S5bQ3)
    h3 Optimism Based on Positive Expectations
    p Student Id: #{ student_id }
    br
    h3 Questions
    br
    h4 Question 3 of 4
      //- span#timerDisplay Time remaining: #{ timer }
    br
    p#question When I am becoming pessimistic or negative about the future, doing these things helps me become more optimistic:
